      <title>刚升大学的高大衔接知识</title>
      <link href="/2025/09/21/Maths/math1/"/>
      <url>/2025/09/21/Maths/math1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="取整函数">取整函数</h2><h3 id="前言">前言</h3><p>在高中的学习中，我们常常研究一些连续性的函数，而忽视了对整数的研究。事实上，整数在数学里也是不可忽视的一部分，毕竟我们最开始接触数学时也是整数，而且整数在高等数学里也是十分重要的研究对象。下面就一起来看看与整数密不可分的函数——取整函数吧</p><h3 id="化小数为整数">化小数为整数</h3><p>假设有一段绳子长5.2m，现在需要几段1m的绳子做标准材料，请问最多能截出多少根标准材料？答案显而易见，是5根。但如果把绳子的长度换成<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span></span>m呢？此时若需要一个数学符号来表示这结果（含<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span></span>），就需要取整函数<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\left [  \right ]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span></span></span></span>出马了。<br>定义：用<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\left [ x \right ]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span></span></span></span>表示不超过<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span></span>的最大整数，即<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&lt;</mo><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mo>≤</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x-1 &lt; \left [ x \right ] \le x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6667em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6835em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">&lt;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span></span><br>例如<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mn>3.4</mn><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\left [ 3.4 \right ] = 3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mord">3.4</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span>，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mn>0.2</mn><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\left [ 0.2 \right ] = 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mord">0.2</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span>，特别注意，<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\left [ x \right ]</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span></span></span></span>是不超过<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">x</span></span></span></span>的最大整数，所以负数应写成这样：<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo fence="true">[</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>2.3</mn><mo fence="true">]</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\left [ -2.3 \right ] = -3</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="minner"><span class="mopen delimcenter" style="top:0em;">[</span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">2.3</span><span class="mclose delimcenter" style="top:0em;">]</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord">3</span></span></span></span><br>这样，我们就完成了小数到整数的转换</p>]]></content>
      
      
